Class SimulationAdjustments

java.lang.Object
simu.model.SimulationAdjustments
public class SimulationAdjustments extends Object
The SimulationAdjustments class provides methods to dynamically adjust various simulation parameters. It includes flags that can be set to adjust the speed of different aspects of the simulation.
